# Controller Kuralları

Controller: parse → validate → delegate → serialize. İş kuralı yok.

## Decorator Stack (Internal Endpoint)

```typescript
@Controller('cases')
export class CaseController {
  @RequirePolicy('case:transition')
  @AuditAction('CASE_TRANSITION')
  @Post(':id/transitions')
  async transition(
    @Param('id') id: string,
    @Body() dto: CreateTransitionDto,
    @CurrentUser() user: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.transitionService.execute({ caseId: id, ...dto, actorUserId: user.id });
  }
}
```

Sıra: `@RequirePolicy` → `@AuditAction` → HTTP method. Public intake/tracking: policy farklı profil.

## DTO Validation

- `class-validator` + global ValidationPipe: `whitelist`, `forbidNonWhitelisted`, `transform`
- Shared schema: `packages/dto` Zod — controller DTO re-export
- Hata: `VALIDATION_FAILED` + field errors

## Response Zarfı

Başarı: `{ data: T }` veya `{ data: [], pagination: {} }`. Controller manuel wrap yapmaz — interceptor halleder.

## Error Handling

`DomainException` → bilinen HTTP status + error code. Controller'da try/catch ile swallow yasak — global filter.

## Anti-pattern'ler

- Controller'da `$transaction`, encrypt/decrypt, policy evaluation
- Endpoint without `@RequirePolicy` (internal)
- Mutating endpoint without `@AuditAction`
- Stack trace / SQL detayı response'a

